ake place after 1 April 2014.</p>","South Northamptonshire","Andrea Leadsom","202688 ; 202724 ; 202726","2014-07-03T15:49:59.2987757Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64273/answer","Biography information for Andrea Leadsom","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64273/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64273/answer",,,,,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2014-06-26","Financial Conduct Authority","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, if he will review the scope of the consumer credit regulatory powers of the Financial Conduct Authority.","false","Biography information for Paul Flynn","Newport West","Paul Flynn","202725"
