"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64045","Department of Health","false","2014-07-02","<p>This is a matter for the National Health Service locally.</p><p> </p><p>We have written to Derek Brown, Chair of the Lancashire Care NHS Foundation Trust informing him of the hon. Member's enquiry. He will reply shortly and a copy of the letter will be placed in the Library.</p><p> </p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison",,"2014-07-02T15:38:39.229962Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64045/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64045/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/64045/answer",,,,,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-06-25","Whyndyke Farm","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what amount has been spent on building the psychiatric facility at Whyndyke Farm to date; and when that facility will become fully operational.","false","Biography information for Sir Mark Hendrick","Preston","Mark Hendrick","202504"
